## Wipeout Analysis
- ~30-40% of games result in total wipeout (score 0.00)
- All 8 agents die at step ~50 (hp starts at 50, drains 1/tick)
- hp.gained = 0 in wipeout games: territory never healed agents
- Hub camp was 20 steps of noop — wasting precious HP time
- Agents spawn within 3 tiles of hub but territory doesn't activate on some maps

