## Key Learnings
- Wipeouts are ~20% of games, map-dependent, affect all policies
- Hub camp (20 steps) is important for territory healing
- Scrambler is effective: 69-106 enemy scrambles per game
- 5 aligners + 1 scrambler (at step 400) is current best config

