## Current Best Config (v112)
- 5 aligners + 1 scrambler at step 400 (4+1 = 5 pressure, 3 miners)
- Hub camp 20 steps, retreat margin 15, deposit threshold 12
- Heart batch: 2 base → 3 at step 500 → 5 at step 2000
- Emergency threshold: min_res < 1 (was 3), emergency budget 3 (was 2)
- Hub proximity bias: strong penalty > 15 tiles from hub
- Expansion bonus: 5.0 per reachable junction (cap 30)
- Defensive scrambler targeting: threat_bonus * 10

