## Bottleneck Analysis
- Heart production: ~335/game = 0.067/step
- Can't brute-force to 10 — need alignments to LAST LONGER
- Ship scrambling is the main threat, slowed by scramblers
- 16 deaths in low-score game vs 0 in high-score game
- Territory doesn't affect ship junction expansion (only via chaining)
